enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve initializing or updating the TreeBuilder instance within the Parser.
The newInstance method creates a new Parser instance with a new TreeBuilder, similar to how setTreeBuilder updates the TreeBuilder.
The getTreeBuilder method retrieves the current TreeBuilder, which can be used to assert the state after calling setTreeBuilder.
After setting the TreeBuilder, the parseInput method can be used to test the parsing behavior with the new TreeBuilder.
